itors = 26\n|nations = 20\n|longnames = yes\n|gold = [[Nawal El Moutawakel]]\n|goldNOC = MAR\n|silver = [[Judi Brown]]\n|silverNOC = USA\n|bronze = [[Cristieana Cojocaru]]\n|bronzeNOC = ROM\n|win_value = 54.61 {{OlyR|athletics}}\n|next = [[Athletics at the 1988 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 400 metres hurdles|1988]]\n}}\n[[Image:TV-icon-2.svg|thumb|110px|'''[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RjiPG1pO8Tk Official Video Highlights]''']]\n\n{{AthleticsAt1984SummerOlympics}}\nThe '''[[Hurdling|Women's 400 metres Hurdles]]''' at the [[Athletics at the 1984 Summer Olympics|1984 Summer Olympics]] in [[Los Angeles, California]] (USA) had an entrylist of 26 competitors, with four qualifying heats (26 runners) and two semifinals (16) before the final (8) took place on August 8, 1984. The women's event was for the first time contested at the [[Olympic Games]].<ref name=\"SR\">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/1984/ATH/womens-400-metres-hurdles.html |title=Athletics at the 1984 Los Angeles Summer Games: Women's 400 metres Hurdles |accessdate=5 October 2017 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>\n\n==Medalists==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\" text-align:center; font-size:110%;\" width=\"35%\"\n|- \n|{{OlympicGoldMedalist|[[Nawal El Moutawakel]]|MAR|1984 Summer}}\n|-\n|{{OlympicSilverMedalist|[[Judi Brown]]|USA|1984 Summer}}\n|-\n|{{OlympicBronzeMedalist|[[Cristieana Cojocaru]]|ROU|1984 Summer}}\n|}\n\n==Abbreviations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\" text-align:center; font-size:110%;\" width=\"35%\"\n|-\n|bgcolor=\"ccffcc\"| '''Q''' || automatic qualification\n|-\n|bgcolor=\"ddffdd\"| '''q''' || qualification by rank\n|-\n|'''DNS''' || did not start\n|-\n|'''NM''' || no mark\n|-\n|'''OR''' || olympic record\n|-\n|'''WR''' || world record\n|-\n|'''AR''' || area record\n|-\n|'''NR''' || national record\n|-\n|'''PB''' || personal best\n|-\n|'''SB''' || season best\n|}\n\n==Final==\n {| border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"2\" cellpadding=\"5\" style=\"border-col